Refund Policy

Effective Date: [Insert Date]

Thank you for shopping with our Multivendor Ecommerce Site ("the Site"). We strive to ensure your satisfaction with every purchase. This Refund Policy outlines the terms and conditions related to refunds for products purchased on the Site. By using our services and making a purchase, you agree to the terms of this Refund Policy.

Refund Eligibility
1.1 Refunds may be issued in the following circumstances:

Product Defect: If the product you received is defective or damaged, you may be eligible for a refund. Please contact our customer support within [insert number of days] days from the date of delivery and provide details and evidence of the defect or damage.

Order Cancellation: If you wish to cancel your order before it has been shipped, you may be eligible for a refund. Please contact our customer support as soon as possible to request the cancellation and refund.

Non-Delivery: If you did not receive your order within the estimated delivery timeframe, you may be eligible for a refund. Please contact our customer support to report the non-delivery and request a refund.

Refund Process
2.1 To request a refund, please contact our customer support within the specified timeframe and provide the necessary details and evidence as requested. Our customer support team will guide you through the refund process.

2.2 Once your refund request is received and reviewed, we will notify you of the status of your refund. If your refund is approved, we will initiate the refund process.

2.3 Refunds will be processed to the original payment method used for the purchase, unless otherwise agreed upon. Please note that it may take some time for the refund to be reflected in your account, depending on your financial institution.

Non-Refundable Items
3.1 The following items are generally non-refundable:

Services: Any services or fees associated with the purchase that have been provided or rendered.

Digital Products: Gift cards, vouchers, or digital products that have been redeemed or used.

Personalized or Customized Items: Products that have been customized or personalized according to your specifications.

Return Shipping Costs
4.1 If a refund is approved due to a product defect, damage, or our error, we will provide a prepaid shipping label or reimburse the return shipping costs.

4.2 If a refund is approved for other reasons such as order cancellation or non-delivery, the return shipping costs will be your responsibility.

Contact Us
